.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-MAX-HTLC-IN-FLIGHT" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-max-htlc-in-flight \- FEAT-1968 channel-max-htlc-in-flight verb
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-max-htlc-in-flight
.I channel_id
.SH DESCRIPTION
channel-max-htlc-in-flight verb for lightning CLI (FEAT-1968).
.PP
Returns the max_total_htlc_value_in_flight_msat for the given channel.
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
